The Levels with a variety of tasks, including: time trial, rocket persecutions, trials in which you will need to show mastery of flying at maximum speeds, as well as research trials. A Modern graphical shell that does not require high resources from a computer, offers modern 2D graphics. Great music, written specifically to create an atmosphere of intense cartoon.
